 the exhibit, which shows the output from the webfilter fortiguard cache dump and webfilter categories commands. Using the output, how can an administrator determine the category of the training.fortinet.com website?", "question_type": "single", "correct_answer": ["B"]}', 'imported', NULL, NULL, '5e5a25ca2239a6cee15f31b7f02a02e077957450800145c40dc4400d9614a057', 1341, '2026-05-04 15:49:15.316442+00', '2026-05-04 15:49:15.600068+00');
