in the Auto Scaling group. This "backlog per instance" value represents the average number of
messages waiting to be processed by each instance.
Then, the CloudOps engineer can create a target tracking policy that automatically scales out or
in based on maintaining a desired backlog threshold. This approach ensures dynamic, workload-
